                     <join result="offenceCrimeDate" targOrder="Y" targets="t18071028-35-off184 t18071028-35-cd185"></join>, a child's great coat, value 5 s. and two handkerchiefs, value 2 s.
            </rs> the property of 
               
                  <persName id="t18071028-35-victim422" type="victimName">
                     John 
                     Derbyshire
                  <interp inst="t18071028-35-victim422" type="surname" value="Derbyshire"></interp>
